---
title: Chicken Satay Burger with potato wedges and peanut salad
description: The tangy peanut sauce that coats the burgers in this dish is bursting with flavour and slightly spicy. Chicken is coated with fragrant spices and zesty lime then fried and sandwiched between two sweet and soft brioche buns, all accompanied by a crisp zingy salad and crunchy potato wedges.
